comments: permits_total = total number of privately-owned housing construction permits issued in the U.S. (thousands)
permits_single_family = number of privately-owned single-family housing construction permits issued in the U.S. (thousands)
starts_total = total number of privately-owned housing units starting construction in the U.S. (thousands)
starts_single_family = number of privately-owned single_family housing units starting construction in the U.S. (thousands)
completed_total = total number of privately-owned housing completed in the U.S. (thousands)
completed_single_family = number of privately-owned single_family housing completed in the U.S. (thousands)
